articles.title: Asteroid will imminently burn up in Earth’s atmosphere over Philippines - CNN
articles.description: A roughly 1-meter asteroid will enter Earth’s atmosphere over the Philippines near Luzon Island at 12:39 p.m. ET, according to the European Space Agency.
